                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310630-313-victim2200 t18310630-313-viclabel1636"></join>, and lodge in Shoreditch. I was removing on the 20th of June from <placeName id="t18310630-313-crimeloc1637">Little Pulteney-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310630-313-crimeloc1637" type="placeName" value="Little Pulteney-street"></interp>
