                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310630-313-off1634 t18310630-313-crimeloc1637"></join> - the prisoner was recommended to me to carry my box; I delivered it to him to carry to <placeName id="t18310630-313-crimeloc1638">Shoreditch</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310630-313-crimeloc1638" type="placeName" value="Shoreditch"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18310630-313-crimeloc1638" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310630-313-off1634 t18310630-313-crimeloc1638"></join> - I was to pay him 1s. 6d.; I went there the same evening, and he had not been - I gave him 2d., and left 1s. 4d. in Mr. Carr's hand to pay him - the box contained all the articles stated; I gave him a written direction - I never saw him till I offered a reward for his apprehension; there were papers in it I would not have taken any money for.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310630-313-person2201">
